archie_en.match_header_quality_desc: The harmonic mean of the teams’ SPI ratings
archie_en.match_header_leverage_desc: How much the result will alter the league projections
archie_en.match_header_combo_desc: The average of quality and importance
archie_en.completed_text_top: After every match, our model calculates three additional metrics for each team.
archie_en.completed_text_bottom:
• Adjusted goals takes into account that not all goals are created equal: A team’s final score is reduced if a goal comes late in a game that it’s leading or when the opponent is a man down. (Meanwhile, goals that are scored in regular situations are adjusted upward to balance out the total number of goals across a league.)
  • Shot-based expected goals (xG) is an estimate of how many goals a team could have scored given the location of its shots and the players who took them.
  • Non-shot expected goals is an estimate of how many goals a team could have scored given their nonshooting actions in and around their opponent’s penalty area.
These three metrics are combined to help generate a team’s SPI rating and therefore its chances of winning future games.
archie_en.tourney_note: The top two teams from each group qualify for the knockout phase.
archie_en.tourney_note2: The third-place team from each group qualifies for the UEFA Europa League knockout phase.
archie_en.tourney_note3: The third-place finisher from each group in the UEFA Champions League — eight teams total — will join the UEFA Europa League in the round of 32.
archie_en.champs_note: The top teams qualify for next season’s UEFA Champions League.
archie_en.promoted_note: The top two teams are automatically promoted, and a third is promoted through a four-team playoff.
archie_en.promoted_note2: The top two teams are automatically promoted, and the third-place team will enter a playoff against the third-to-last team from the higher division to determine if it is promoted.
archie_en.promoted_note3: The top three teams are automatically promoted, and a fourth is promoted through a four-team playoff.
archie_en.relegated_note: The bottom teams are relegated.
archie_en.relegated_note2: The bottom two teams are automatically relegated, and the third-to-last team will enter a playoff against the third-place team from the lower division to determine if it is relegated.
archie_en.relegated_note3: The bottom three teams are automatically relegated, and the fourth-to-last team will enter a playoff against a team from the lower division to determine if it is relegated.
archie_en.mls_note: The top six teams from each conference — 12 teams total — make the MLS playoffs. The top two teams from each conference receive a first-round bye.
archie_en.usl_note: The top eight teams from each conference — 16 teams total — make the USL playoffs.
archie_en.ligamx_note: The top eight teams at the end of the regular season make the Liga MX playoffs.
archie_en.nwsl_note: The top four teams at the end of the regular season make the NWSL playoffs.
archie_en.aleague_note: The top six teams make the A-League playoffs, with two teams receiving a first-round bye.
archie_en.serieb_note: Three teams are promoted, and four teams are relegated. Depending on the league standings, playoffs for the final promotion and relegation spots may be necessary.
archie_en.argentina_note: Four teams — based on overall performance during the last four seasons — are relegated.
archie_en.norway_note: The bottom two teams are automatically relegated, and the third-to-last team will enter a playoff against a team from the lower division to determine if it is relegated.
archie_en.scotland_note: The bottom team is automatically relegated, and the second-to-last team will enter a playoff against a team from the lower division to determine if it is relegated.
archie_en.netherlands_note: The bottom team is automatically relegated, and the next two bottom teams will enter a playoff against teams from the lower division to determine if they are relegated.
archie_en.denmark_note: One to three teams are relegated through a playoff.
archie_en.methodology_sentence: Read more about the methodology behind these forecasts and how we rated the quality and importance of each match.

archie_es.dek: Pronóstico y SPI ratings de <x> ligas, actualizado luego de cada partido.
archie_es.match_header_quality_desc: El promedio armónico de las SPI de los equipos
archie_es.match_header_leverage_desc: Cuánto el resultado cambiará las predicciones de la liga
archie_es.match_header_combo_desc: El promedio de calidad e importancia
archie_es.primary_probabilities: Probabilidades al final de la temporada
archie_es.completed_text_top: Luego de cada partido, nuestro modelo calcula tres métricas adicionales para cada equipo para evaluar su desempeño.
archie_es.completed_text_bottom: Goles ajustados reduce el valor de goles al final del partido cuando un equipo está ganando y su oponente tiene un jugador menos. Goles por tiros es un estimado de cuántos goles un equipo puede anotar dada su locación en los tiros y los jugadores que los realizan, y Tiros sin gol es un estimado de cuántos goles un equipo puede hacer tomando en cuenta sus acciones sin tirar al arco y alrededor del área penal de su oponente. Estas métricas avanzadas se combinan con el marcador actual del partido, afectando el puesto de cada equipo y predicciones futuras.
archie_es.tourney_note: Los dos mejores equipos de cada grupo se clasifican para la fase de eliminación directa.
archie_es.tourney_note2: El tercer puesto de cada grupo se clasifica para la fase de eliminación directa de la Europa League.
archie_es.tourney_note3: Ocho equipos de la Champions League se unen a la Europa League en la ronda de 32.
archie_es.champs_note: Los equipos principales se clasifican para la próxima temporada de la Champions League.
archie_es.mls_note: Los mejores seis equipos de cada conferencia — 12 clubes en total — se clasifican a los playoffs de MLS. Los dos mejores de cada conferencia pasan automáticamente a la primera ronda.
archie_es.ligamx_note: Los ocho mejores equipos al final de la campaña regular se clasifican para la liguilla de la Liga MX.
archie_es.nwsl_note: Los cuatro mejores equipos al final de la campaña regular se clasifican para la liguilla de la NWSL.

archie_pt.headline: Previsões dos times de futebol
archie_pt.dek: Previsões e classificação SPI das ligas, atualizadas ao fim de cada partida
archie_pt.match_header_quality_desc: A média harmônica do SPI dos times
archie_pt.match_header_leverage_desc: Quanto o resultado afetará as previsões da liga
archie_pt.match_header_combo_desc: A média entre qualidade e importância
archie_pt.completed_text_top: Ao fim de cada jogo, nosso modelo calcula três métricas adicionais de cada equipe para avaliar seu desempenho.
archie_pt.completed_text_bottom: Ajuste de Gols reduz o valor de gols ao fim do jogo quando uma equipe está ganhando e seu oponente tem um jogador a menos. Gols por chute É uma estimativa de quantos gols uma equipe pode fazer dada a localização dos chutes e os jogadores que finalizaram, e Chutes sem gol é uma estimativa de quantos gols uma equipe pode fazer levando em conta seus passes e ao redor da área de seu oponente. Essas métricas avançadas se combinam com o placar atual do jogo, afetando a posição de cada equipe e também futuras previsões.
archie_pt.tourney_note: Os dois melhores times de cada grupo se classificam para a fase de mata-mata.
archie_pt.tourney_note2: O time de terceiro lugar de cada grupo se classificam à fase de mata-mata da Europa League.
archie_pt.tourney_note3: Oito times da Champions League vão para a Europa League na rodada de 32.
archie_pt.champs_note: Os primeiros colocados se classificam para a próxima temporada da Champions League.
archie_pt.mls_note: Os seis times mais bem colocados de cada conferência - 12 times - se classificam aos playoffs da MLS. Os dois melhores de cada conferência folgam automaticamente na primeira rodada e avançam direto para a segunda fase.
archie_pt.ligamx_note: Os oito melhores times ao fim da fase regular se classificam aos playoffs da Liga MX.
archie_pt.nwsl_note: Os quatro melhores times ao fim de cada fase regular se classificam aos playoffs da NWSL.
